snippet.title: ANANTA | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
#ananta  #projectmugen 
Wait, did I just see a toilet racing next to the Wind Drop driver?
Forget the plans and the rules—let's just have a blast!
Time to hit up Nova City and unleash the fun!

Ananta has now opened pre-registration on our official website. Click the link to sign up for the game and receive the latest news.
https://www.anantagame.com/preview/

For game updates and events, follow us: 
Discord: https://discord.gg/ananta
X: https://x.com/Ananta_EN
Facebook: www.facebook.com/ananta.en
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ananta.global/
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/AnantaOfficial/

♪BGM：milet - 「SEVENTH HEAVEN」
